criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult patients (age >18 years) with acute pancreatitis according to the revised
             Atlanta criteria;12

          -  Informed consent;

          -  Known time of debut of symptoms.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic pancreatitis;

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Known malignant disease;

          -  More than 72 hours from debut of symptoms to inclusion.
